{"tid":1576305,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發]政府將成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-09-17T07:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T08:00:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6405b942dcd5a6a0c1345a43847e8e80e60d4799","tid":1576305,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"調查東鐵出軌事故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d8632614a08eeacf94e790f54b3596c720342f","tid":1576305,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"8f5e1394971752861be23b75ed7fa7bbec6c0ffd","tid":1576305,"uid":74990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vAQ-_RwswBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvAQ-_RwswBs&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=d58cb308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vAQ-_RwswBs</a>"},{"pid":"81704e056ac2bac76755a55486819d25f9115c59","tid":1576305,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:36:21.000Z","msg":"...<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62e04e7c15a53c4ccb34cdb9dc96f3ff405b0d3","tid":1576305,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"現時列車服務安排 Current train service arrangements<br />\n➡️ <a href=\"http://metroride.hk/2lQaKWl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmetroride.hk%2F2lQaKWl&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=1a3de50d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">metroride.hk/2lQaKWl</a><br />\n<br />\n＃＃＃＃＃<br />\n<br />\n初步資料顯示，東鐵綫由落馬洲開出的列車，約於 0830 時在紅磡站附近出軌，這班 L094 列車的 12 個車廂中，至少 3 個車廂出軌，頭卡已進入該站 1 號月台<br />\n<br />\n車廂分離後列車迅即停低，但由於車上電綫經已扯斷，所以未能一次過發出疏散指示<br />\n<br />\n事件中，一對車門 及 一段路軌 同告損壞，有乘客經這對車門落路軌逃生，期間他們亦用緊急門掣開啟其他車門，但無人按車外指示打開緊急逃生梯<br />\n<br />\n期間共有八名乘客輕傷，緊急服務人員亦協助乘客疏散<br />\n<br />\n涉事列車為「中期翻新列車」，由英國生產並於 1982 年投入服務；<br />\n<br />\n行車訊號為法國 ALSTOM 的「TBL」系統，而昨晚的路軌工程亦無牽涉這段路軌<br />\n<br />\n出軌原因仍有待確定，車輪缺損 或 路軌斷裂 皆有可能，機電工程署將成立獨立調查委員會，跟進事件<br />\n<br />\n而出軌的車廂會於署方完成初步調查、蒐證後，吊離事發現場，目前港鐵公司未能公佈東鐵綫全綫恢復通車的時間<br />\n<br />\n－<br />\n<br />\nBy the initial information, an East Rail Line service L094 which originated from Lok Ma Chau derailed near Hung Hom at ~0830 hours <br />\n<br />\nAt least 3 of 12 carriages derailed with the 1st carriage entered Platform 1 there and a pair of train doors was damaged <br />\n<br />\nThe train stopped immediately when carriages were disconnected and no centralised evacuation order can be made due to inter-car wires were ruptured<br />\n<br />\nA pair of train doors and a piece of rail also found damaged, while passengers descended onto tracks through this door<br />\n<br />\nDuring the course, passengers also opened other doors through emergency handles however no detrainment ladders deployed by the instruction displayed outside carriages<br />\n<br />\n8 passengers received minor injuries in total and emergency service also assisted their evacuations<br />\n<br />\nThe train involved is a Mid-Life Refurbishment Train manufactured in Great Britain and put into service since 1982<br />\n<br />\nThe current signalling system is &quot;TBL&quot; which made by French-based ALSTOM while the rail replacement work yesterday night did not include this section of tracks<br />\n<br />\nThe reason of this derailment is not known. Wheel defect or cracked rail are possible clauses. An independent investigation will be established by the EMSD of HKSAR Gov<br />\n<br />\nDerailment carriages will then be lifted away when EMSD finishes their preliminary evidence searches <br />\n<br />\nThe #MTR Corporation is unable to provide any estimated resumption time of full East Rail Line services in the stage<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/188207124523573/posts/3291601810850740?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F188207124523573%2Fposts%2F3291601810850740%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2F21VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=5b52c197\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/188207124523573/posts/3291601810850740?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"83baa9f08e653c3b9fba0153f420e9f957acb6b0","tid":1576305,"uid":266635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221700a85f17f71a6fce5c56d4a39816d8c455dd","tid":1576305,"uid":70403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:37:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好覆 不推文</span>"},{"pid":"6656b42eaf13b3828defaddf924f2178ceeaa960","tid":1576305,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"陳煩講係黨鐵內部唔係法定果個"},{"pid":"7c92cdcbf600aaca2ea7b0947a7615609576a333","tid":1576305,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:39:17.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 茉莉花園<br />\n 無撚聊"},{"pid":"3cb5baf4994712c8d6a7f49be573e72351b0a1a5","tid":1576305,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 茉莉花園<br />\n無撚聊"},{"pid":"75a71f196797deaa1665bd70022bd41e1c4f61d5","tid":1576305,"uid":180716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2